2001-07-11  Shane Caraveo  <shane@php.net>

    * ext/standard/var.c:
    prevent php from crashing when serializing circular data.

    This script produced the crash.
    <?
    $hash["test_key"] = "test_value";
    $hash["hash_key"] = &$hash;
    echo serialize($hash);
    ?>

